# Accounts pool: the SQLite DB holds plaintext credentials + cookie backups, and
# the per-account Chrome profile dirs hold live sessions. These live in
# ~/.pytok by default (outside the repo); guard against a stray copy or a
# $PYTOK_HOME pointed at the tree ever being committed.
*.db
.pytok/
profiles/